title: Lamb Shortloin, Bacon Crumble & Roasted Potatoes for Dinner with a Chocolate Toffee Pudding for Dessert
description: Sear a tender and succulent lamb loin that's just right for a gourmet-style dinner. With all the flavour of nostalgic roast lamb, plus wholesome veggies, it's sure to have you feeling festive with every delicious mouthful of this Christmas in July special. And the best feasts end with a sweet treat, so we've included a serving of chocolate toffee pudding with poached pears for dessert!

